{"tid":59371,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[台北]一月頭去7日6夜,求合家歡行程介紹","createTime":"2016-12-29T14:56:33.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-31T06:40:54.000Z","uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"54a93af29f2619c46f2b9f12f13a614dde10cb2b","tid":59371,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:56:33.000Z","msg":"其實都係同阿爸阿媽去,無老人家<br />\n唔洗話太怕麻煩<br />\n<br />\n暫時淨係諗到四日(不分次序)<br />\n-落機果日去到西門町酒店SETTLE好應該下晝4,5點左右,應該會鳩行-下再食個晚飯(有咩推介??)<br />\n-淡水<br />\n-九份十分猴桐果堆(會包車, 以前自己去搭平溪線辛苦到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n-貓空動物園(但唔知搭D咩好,夜晚去夜市?邊間?)<br />\n<br />\n仲有兩日要諗, 最尾果日雖然搭夜機,但廢事周圍騰,應該都係起西門町行下,食個晚飯再包車去機場算)<br />\n<br />\n有無熟路巴打有推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dabb5ab8581eb3e30b1307789aa6b22b0ed8bb4","tid":59371,"uid":5429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T15:08:33.000Z","msg":"淡水嘅TNT 炭燒牛排 正 淡水站一出望到m記隔離就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a8adb23f07f0a76316f3e22686f0134952cb195","tid":59371,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T15:16:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淡水嘅TNT 炭燒牛排 正 淡水站一出望到m記隔離就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好, 我淡水果日都未PLAN食咩好,就呢間"},{"pid":"5d29e56f13c9b5c802d1b99ab28ce61b0a98c6ff","tid":59371,"uid":31847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T15:44:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>淡水嘅TNT 炭燒牛排 正 淡水站一出望到m記隔離就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好, 我淡水果日都未PLAN食咩好,就呢間</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n淡水有間蛋糕鋪好似好出名，好多人排隊果間就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋想輕鬆下可以搭船去對面岸踩下單車既，有幾款一齊踩果d"},{"pid":"caf1eb31af1091b00aab3e3ad582040daae77831","tid":59371,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:50:49.000Z","msg":"MITSUI OUTLET值唔值得去??"},{"pid":"84017e5ec27c2c949282b4d306e57e49ab87c486","tid":59371,"uid":68553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:38:48.000Z","msg":"可以去玩飛行傘， 上引水產<br />\n<br />\n動物園可以搭捷運去有個站叫動物園的"},{"pid":"51cc2e6667d51ce955b55acd38a05e7e192ee6dd","tid":59371,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T16:41:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以去玩飛行傘， 上引水產<br />\n<br />\n動物園可以搭捷運去有個站叫動物園的</blockquote><br />\n上引水產連登仔個個都話伏咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef9d36ecabf3a8a75e7bb1297b46d5ff4e445f0","tid":59371,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T16:41:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可以去玩飛行傘， 上引水產<br />\n<br />\n動物園可以搭捷運去有個站叫動物園的</blockquote><br />\n上引水產連登仔個個都話伏咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n動物園果D 我意思係唔知配搭D咩行程好, 深坑老街?"},{"pid":"514204aca706017872bb4e9d575d7b53314634c5","tid":59371,"uid":24167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T17:57:43.000Z","msg":"林森北路"},{"pid":"5fda73c7daaddc75dc605120c750b9a3cfc05580","tid":59371,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:40:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>林森北路</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> GOOGLE D結果咁多色情野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}